description:
This market will resolve to “Human” or “AI” based on which team has the higher Team ROI at the end of the Aster Human vs AI trading competition season 2.

The Team ROI values displayed on the official Aster competition page will be used for resolution.

If both teams have the same Team ROI at the time the competition ends, this market will resolve 50-50.

The primary resolution source will be the official Aster Human vs AI page:
https://www.asterdex-testnet.com/en/campaigns/human-vs-ai

If the competition is not completed or the official Team ROI data is unavailable, the market will remain open until reliable data is published by Aster. If no such data is available by March 31, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, the market will resolve 50-50.
